                <h1 class="nhsuk-u-margin-bottom-5">Warning callout</h1>
                <p class="nhsuk-body-l">The warning callout is designed to stand out from the rest of the content.</p>
                <p class="nhsuk-u-margin-bottom-8">It helps users identify and understand the important content on the page, even if they don't read the whole page.</p>
